Text: "Why Portugal. 10 years ago, when people said let\u2019s go to Portugal, I will\
  \ be \u201Cok, let me see where it is\u201D. But nowadays I will say \u201C oh yeah,\
  \ I have brother, sister, friends, aunty, uncle and even neighbors that were recently\
  \ visit Portugal and it was a great unique place to go\u201D. Ok, let\u2019s see\
  \ what must see and do when we visit Portugal. What makes this place one country\
  \ that we must visit?"
